Hello, I'm not an eslint member. But, In my opinion, it looks like a bug. reproduced- [demo](https://eslint.org/demo#)

```
/* eslint multiline-comment-style: ["error"] */
/*
  // a line comment
  some.code();
*/
```
after fix. -> `Parsing error: Unterminated regular expression`.
```js
/* eslint multiline-comment-style: ["error"] */
/*
 *// a line comment
 *some.code();
 */
```
